name: VOLYA IS UKRAINE
description:
The word Volya means freadom and it is hidden inside the ukrainian Trident. 

Ukraine is an independant country that is built on democratic freedoms. We are able to riot, overthrow, we have independant media and freedom of speach. 
Ukraine will never go under propagandistic and ignorant Russian tyrant. 

This art work is made by Marina Samohina, Ukrainian artist from eastern Ukraine that has been occupied by the Russians for 8 years now. Now when attack of Russian troops is spreading all over Ukraine Marina agreed to join Volya and donate money raised to buy body armour for Ukrainian soldiers.
